SELECT
  `TDM`.`FLD_DOC_ID`             AS `FLD_DOC_ID`
  , 'Sales'                      AS `Sales`
  , `TDILD`.`FLD_LINE_NUM`       AS `FLD_LINE_NUM`
  , `TDM`.`FLD_DOC_DATE`         AS `FLD_DOC_DATE`
  ,  IF(TDM.`FLD_PRICE_LEVEL_ID`=69,'E-Commerce(EC)',`TDCD`.`FLD_TYPE_DESC`)       AS `FLD_TYPE_DESC`
  , `TDCD`.`FLD_CONTACT_ID`      AS `PARTNER_SITE_INT_ID`
  , `TIM`.`FLD_PRINT_NAME`       AS `FLD_PRINT_NAME`
  , (CASE `TIM`.`FLD_ITEM_TYPE` WHEN 1 THEN 'New' WHEN 18 THEN IF((`TIM`.`FLD_EXCHANGE_TYPE` = 1),'New','Upgrade') WHEN 2 THEN 'Upgrade' WHEN 12 THEN 'TSS Coupon' WHEN 43 THEN IF((`TSIAM`.`FLD_ADDON_TYPE` = 1),'TSS','Addon') WHEN 44 THEN 'Rental' WHEN 45 THEN 'TDE' WHEN 47 THEN 'Addon Subs' WHEN 21 THEN 'Registration Charge' END) AS `PRODUCT_TYPE`
  , `TDILD`.`FLD_ITEM_QTY`       AS `FLD_ITEM_QTY`
  , (CASE `TDM`.`FLD_DOC_IN_INTERFACE` WHEN 1 THEN 'Intranet' WHEN 2 THEN 'Extranet' WHEN 3 THEN 'Tally' WHEN 4 THEN 'Internal trigger' WHEN 5 THEN 'Partner portal' END) AS `INTERFACE_TYPE`
  , (IF((`TDM`.`FLD_CURRENCY_CODE` = 1),IF((`TDM`.`FLD_DOC_TYPE` = 1),-(`TDILD`.`FLD_AMOUNT`),`TDILD`.`FLD_AMOUNT`),ROUND(IF((`TDM`.`FLD_DOC_TYPE` = 1),(-(`TDILD`.`FLD_AMOUNT`) * `TDM`.`FLD_FOREX_RATE`),(`TDILD`.`FLD_AMOUNT` * `TDM`.`FLD_FOREX_RATE`)),2)) - IF((`TDILD`.`FLD_LINE_NUM` = 1),IF((`TDM`.`FLD_DOC_TYPE` = 1),-(IFNULL(`B`.`FLD_LEDGER_AMOUNT`,0)),IFNULL(`B`.`FLD_LEDGER_AMOUNT`,0)),0)) AS `AMOUNT`
  , `TPM`.`FLD_PERIOD_TEXT`      AS `FLD_FORTNIGHT`
  , `TPM_M`.`FLD_PERIOD_TEXT`    AS `FLD_MONTH`
  , `TPM_Q`.`FLD_PERIOD_TEXT`    AS `FLD_QTR`
  , `TPM_Y`.`FLD_PERIOD_TEXT`    AS `FLD_YEAR`
  , IFNULL(`TADCGRL`.`FLD_REGION_NAME`,`TCCRM`.`FLD_REGION_NAME`) AS `DOC_REGION`
  , IFNULL(`TADCGRL`.`FLD_ZONE_NAME`,`TCCRM_ZD`.`FLD_REGION_NAME`) AS `DOC_ZONE`
  , `TADCGRL`.`FLD_COUNTRY_NAME` AS `DOC_COUNTRY_NAME`
  , TIPLM.`FLD_NAME` AS FLD_PRICE_LEVEL
  , TDDD.`FLD_DISCOUNT_PERCENTAGE` AS FLD_DISCOUNT_PERCENTAGE 
FROM ((((((((((((((`tallydb`.`TBL_DOCV_MASTER` `TDM`
                JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_DOCV_ITEM_LINE_DETAILS` `TDILD`
                  ON ((`TDM`.`FLD_DOC_ID` = `TDILD`.`FLD_DOC_ID`)))
               LEFT JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_DOCV_LEDGER_DETAILS` `B`
                 ON (((`TDM`.`FLD_DOC_ID` = `B`.`FLD_DOC_ID`)
                      AND (`B`.`FLD_LEDGER_TYPE` = 3)
                      AND (`B`.`FLD_LEDGER_ID` = 1604))))
              JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_ITEM_MASTER` `TIM`
                ON ((`TDILD`.`FLD_ITEM_ID` = `TIM`.`FLD_ITEM_ID`)))
             LEFT JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_SD_IM_ADDON_MASTER` `TSIAM`
               ON ((`TIM`.`FLD_ADDON_ID` = `TSIAM`.`FLD_ADDON_ID`)))
            JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_DOC_CONTACT_DETAILS` `TDCD`
              ON ((`TDM`.`FLD_INVOICE_TO_CONTACT_KEY` = `TDCD`.`FLD_DOC_CONTACT_KEY`)))
           JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_PERIOD_MASTER` `TPM`
             ON (((`TDM`.`FLD_DOC_DATE` >= `TPM`.`FLD_PERIOD_START_DATE`)
                  AND (`TDM`.`FLD_DOC_DATE` <= `TPM`.`FLD_PERIOD_END_DATE`)
                  AND (`TPM`.`FLD_PERIOD_TYPE` = 3))))
          JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_PERIOD_MASTER` `TPM_M`
            ON ((`TPM`.`FLD_MONTH_ID` = `TPM_M`.`FLD_PERIOD_ID`)))
         JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_PERIOD_MASTER` `TPM_Q`
           ON ((`TPM`.`FLD_QTR_ID` = `TPM_Q`.`FLD_PERIOD_ID`)))
        JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_PERIOD_MASTER` `TPM_Y`
          ON ((`TPM`.`FLD_YEAR_ID` = `TPM_Y`.`FLD_PERIOD_ID`)))
       LEFT JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_AGGR_PARTNER_INFO_SUMMARY` `TAPIS`
         ON (((`TDCD`.`FLD_CONTACT_ID` = `TAPIS`.`FLD_ACCOUNT_SITE_INTERNAL_ID`)
              AND (`TAPIS`.`FLD_ACCOUNT_SITE_INTERNAL_ID` > 0))))
      LEFT JOIN `tallydbaggregation`.`TBL_AGGR_DOMESTIC_CITY_GEO_REGION_LIST` `TADCGRL`
        ON ((`TDCD`.`FLD_CITY_ID` = `TADCGRL`.`FLD_CITY_ID`)))
     LEFT JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_CRM_CONTACT_REGION_MASTER` `TCCRM`
       ON ((`TDM`.`FLD_REGION_ID` = `TCCRM`.`FLD_REGION_ID`)))
    LEFT JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_CRM_CONTACT_REGION_GROUP_LINK` `TCCRGL_ZD`
      ON (((`TCCRM`.`FLD_REGION_ID` = `TCCRGL_ZD`.`FLD_REGION_ID`)
           AND (`TCCRGL_ZD`.`FLD_LOGICAL_REGION_FLAG` = 1)
           AND (`TCCRGL_ZD`.`FLD_CURR_FLAG` = 1)
           AND ISNULL(`TCCRGL_ZD`.`FLD_END_DATE`))))
   LEFT JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_CRM_CONTACT_REGION_MASTER` `TCCRM_ZD`
     ON ((`TCCRGL_ZD`.`FLD_PARENT_REGION_ID` = `TCCRM_ZD`.`FLD_REGION_ID`)))
	LEFT JOIN TBL_ITEM_PRICE_LEVEL_MASTER TIPLM
	ON TIPLM.`FLD_PRICE_LEVEL_ID`=TDM.`FLD_PRICE_LEVEL_ID`
   LEFT JOIN TBL_DOC_DISCOUNT_DETAILS TDDD
	ON TDDD.`FLD_DOC_ID`=TDM.FLD_DOC_ID
WHERE ((`TDM`.`FLD_DOC_TYPE` IN(1,6,7))
       AND (`TDILD`.`FLD_BUSS_TRANS_TYPE` NOT IN(17,22))
       AND (`TDM`.`FLD_CANCEL_FLAG` = 0)
       AND (`TDM`.`FLD_DOC_DATE` >= '2025-04-01')-- change date back to 2017-04-01
       AND (`TDM`.`FLD_DOC_DATE` <= CURDATE())
		AND (`TDM`.`FLD_DOC_ID` NOT IN (  SELECT 
  DISTINCT FLD_DOC_ID
FROM
  `TBL_DOCV_MASTER` A 
WHERE A.`FLD_DOC_DATE` >= '2024-01-01' 
  AND A.`FLD_DOC_TYPE` = 6 
  AND A.`FLD_DOC_FULL_NUM` LIKE 'TDP/%' 
  AND A.`FLD_COMPANY_ID` = 100162
  AND A.`FLD_PRICE_LEVEL_ID` = 21)
  AND
  TDM.`FLD_DOC_ID` NOT IN (
		SELECT DISTINCT FLD_DOC_ID
		FROM `TBL_DOCV_MASTER` A 
		WHERE A.`FLD_DOC_DATE` >= '2025-04-01' 
		  AND A.`FLD_DOC_TYPE` = 6 
		  AND FLD_DOC_FULL_NUM REGEXP '^S/[0-9]+/[0-9]{2}-[0-9]{2}$'
		  AND A.`FLD_COMPANY_ID` = 100000
		  AND A.`FLD_PRICE_LEVEL_ID` = 21
		  AND A.`FLD_DOC_IN_INTERFACE`=1
		  )
 
))
GROUP BY `TDM`.`FLD_DOC_ID`,`TDILD`.`FLD_LINE_NUM` UNION ALL SELECT
                                                               `TDVSM`.`FLD_DOC_ID`            AS `FLD_DOC_ID`
                                                               , 'CR/DR Price Diff'            AS `CR/DR Price Diff`
                                                               , `TDVSD`.`FLD_DOC_LINE_NUM`    AS `FLD_DOC_LINE_NUM`
                                                               , `TDVSM`.`FLD_DOC_DATE`        AS `FLD_DOC_DATE`
                                                               , 'Distributor'                 AS `Distributor`
                                                               , `TDVSM`.`FLD_CONTACT_ID`      AS `FLD_CONTACT_ID`
                                                               , `TIM`.`FLD_PRINT_NAME`        AS `FLD_PRINT_NAME`
                                                               , (CASE `TIM`.`FLD_ITEM_TYPE` WHEN 1 THEN 'New' WHEN 18 THEN IF((`TIM`.`FLD_EXCHANGE_TYPE` = 1),'New','Upgrade') WHEN 2 THEN 'Upgrade' WHEN 12 THEN 'TSS Coupon' WHEN 43 THEN IF((`TSIAM`.`FLD_ADDON_TYPE` = 1),'TSS','Addon') WHEN 44 THEN 'Rental' WHEN 45 THEN 'TDE' WHEN 47 THEN 'Addon Subs' WHEN 21 THEN 'Registration Charge' END) AS `PRODUCT_TYPE`
                                                               , 1                             AS `qTY`
                                                               , 'Intranet'                    AS `Intranet`
                                                               , IF((`TDVSD`.`FLD_SETTLEMENT_TYPE` = 1),-(`TDVSD`.`FLD_AMOUNT`),`TDVSD`.`FLD_AMOUNT`) AS `FLD_AMOUNT`
                                                               , `TPM`.`FLD_PERIOD_TEXT`       AS `FLD_FORTNIGHT`
                                                               , `TPM_M`.`FLD_PERIOD_TEXT`     AS `FLD_MONTH`
                                                               , `TPM_Q`.`FLD_PERIOD_TEXT`     AS `FLD_QTR`
                                                               , `TPM_Y`.`FLD_PERIOD_TEXT`     AS `FLD_YEAR`
                                                               , `TCCRM`.`FLD_REGION_NAME`     AS `DOC_REGION`
                                                               , `TCCRM_ZD`.`FLD_REGION_NAME`  AS `DOC_ZONE`
                                                               , `TAPIS`.`FLD_COUNTRY_NAME`    AS `DOC_COUNTRY_NAME`
																, NULL AS FLD_PRICE_LEVEL
							       								, NULL AS FLD_DISCOUNT_PERCENTAGE
                                                             FROM (((((((((((`tallydb`.`TBL_DOC_VOUCHER_SETTLEMENT_MASTER` `TDVSM`
                                                                          JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_DOC_VOUCHER_SETTLEMENT_DETAILS` `TDVSD`
                                                                            ON ((`TDVSM`.`FLD_DOC_ID` = `TDVSD`.`FLD_DOC_ID`)))
                                                                         JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_ITEM_MASTER` `TIM`
                                                                           ON ((`TDVSD`.`FLD_ITEM_ID` = `TIM`.`FLD_ITEM_ID`)))
                                                                        LEFT JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_SD_IM_ADDON_MASTER` `TSIAM`
                                                                          ON ((`TIM`.`FLD_ADDON_ID` = `TSIAM`.`FLD_ADDON_ID`)))
                                                                       JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_PERIOD_MASTER` `TPM`
                                                                         ON (((`TDVSM`.`FLD_DOC_DATE` >= `TPM`.`FLD_PERIOD_START_DATE`)
                                                                              AND (`TDVSM`.`FLD_DOC_DATE` <= `TPM`.`FLD_PERIOD_END_DATE`)
                                                                              AND (`TPM`.`FLD_PERIOD_TYPE` = 3))))
                                                                      JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_PERIOD_MASTER` `TPM_M`
                                                                        ON ((`TPM`.`FLD_MONTH_ID` = `TPM_M`.`FLD_PERIOD_ID`)))
                                                                     JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_PERIOD_MASTER` `TPM_Q`
                                                                       ON ((`TPM`.`FLD_QTR_ID` = `TPM_Q`.`FLD_PERIOD_ID`)))
                                                                    JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_PERIOD_MASTER` `TPM_Y`
                                                                      ON ((`TPM`.`FLD_YEAR_ID` = `TPM_Y`.`FLD_PERIOD_ID`)))
                                                                   LEFT JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_CRM_CONTACT_REGION_MASTER` `TCCRM`
                                                                     ON ((`TDVSM`.`FLD_REGION_ID` = `TCCRM`.`FLD_REGION_ID`)))
                                                                  LEFT JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_CRM_CONTACT_REGION_GROUP_LINK` `TCCRGL_ZD`
                                                                    ON (((`TCCRM`.`FLD_REGION_ID` = `TCCRGL_ZD`.`FLD_REGION_ID`)
                                                                         AND (`TCCRGL_ZD`.`FLD_LOGICAL_REGION_FLAG` = 1)
                                                                         AND (`TCCRGL_ZD`.`FLD_CURR_FLAG` = 1)
                                                                         AND ISNULL(`TCCRGL_ZD`.`FLD_END_DATE`))))
                                                                 LEFT JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_CRM_CONTACT_REGION_MASTER` `TCCRM_ZD`
                                                                   ON ((`TCCRGL_ZD`.`FLD_PARENT_REGION_ID` = `TCCRM_ZD`.`FLD_REGION_ID`)))
                                                                LEFT JOIN `tallydb`.`TBL_AGGR_PARTNER_INFO_SUMMARY` `TAPIS`
                                                                  ON (((`TDVSM`.`FLD_CONTACT_ID` = `TAPIS`.`FLD_ACCOUNT_SITE_INTERNAL_ID`)
                                                                       AND (`TAPIS`.`FLD_ACCOUNT_SITE_INTERNAL_ID` > 0))))
                                                             WHERE ((`TDVSM`.`FLD_DOC_DATE` >= '2017-07-01')
                                                                    AND (`TDVSM`.`FLD_DOC_DATE` <= CURDATE())
                                                                    AND (`TDVSM`.`FLD_CANCEL_FLAG` = 0)
                                                                    AND (`TDVSM`.`FLD_CONTACT_TYPE` = 14))
                                                             GROUP BY `TDVSM`.`FLD_DOC_ID`,`TDVSD`.`FLD_DOC_LINE_NUM`;

SELECT 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`FLD_DOC_ID`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`Sales`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`FLD_LINE_NUM`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`FLD_DOC_DATE`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`FLD_TYPE_DESC`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`PARTNER_SITE_INT_ID`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`FLD_PRINT_NAME`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`PRODUCT_TYPE`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`FLD_ITEM_QTY`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`INTERFACE_TYPE`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`AMOUNT`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`FLD_FORTNIGHT`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`FLD_MONTH`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`FLD_QTR`, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`FLD_YEAR`, 
  REPLACE( IFNULL(`TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`DOC_REGION`,`TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`DOC_REGION`), '&', 'and' ) AS DOC_REGION, 
  `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.`DOC_ZONE`
FROM `TBL_SALES_REVENUE` 
ORDER BY `TBL_SALES_REVENUE`.PARTNER_SITE_INT_ID
